schemas.name: query.type.graphql
schemas.content:
type Query {

  # This query returns the Snippet matching the given id
  getSnippetById(id: ID!): Snippet

  # This query returns all stored Snippets
  getSnippets: [Snippet],

  # This query return the last (count) Snippets ordered by descending creation date
  getLastSnippets(count: Int): [Snippet]

}
